  <entry>
    <title>&lt;프로그래머스&gt; 배열의 평균값</title>
    <link href="http://mjae404.github.io/2024/05/05/programmers-012/"/>
    <id>http://mjae404.github.io/2024/05/05/programmers-012/</id>
    <published>2024-05-05T04:58:43.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-05T05:07:50.162Z</updated>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;정수 배열 &lt;code&gt;numbers&lt;/code&gt;가 매개변수로 주어집니다. &lt;code&gt;numbers&lt;/code&gt;의 원소의 평균값을 return하도록 solution 함수를 완성해주세요.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;0 ≤ &lt;code&gt;numbers&lt;/code&gt;의 원소 ≤ 1,000 &lt;/li&gt;
